00:36:36.233 --> 00:36:37.434
This is severe malnutrition.

00:36:37.754 --> 00:36:38.713
He needs to recuperate.

00:36:39.073 --> 00:36:40.233
Just an IV drip today.

00:36:41.113 --> 00:36:42.874
When you go back, tell him to rest.

00:36:43.128 --> 00:36:44.633
Balanced diet. Small frequent meals.

00:36:45.874 --> 00:36:46.374
Okay.

00:36:47.553 --> 00:36:49.474
Can you be more specific?

00:36:52.914 --> 00:36:54.834
Just to meet the basic needs of society.

00:36:54.834 --> 00:36:57.233
- The debate rehearsal has started?
- Yes.

00:36:57.673 --> 00:36:59.113
Should I go in and ask them to stop?

00:36:59.113 --> 00:37:00.033
The watchdog theory...

00:37:00.033 --> 00:37:01.754
No, we'll just listen.

00:37:01.914 --> 00:37:02.593
What problem?

00:37:02.754 --> 00:37:04.633
Of course, there's a problem.

00:37:05.073 --> 00:37:05.994
In today's China,

00:37:06.394 --> 00:37:07.673
on the land beneath our feet,

00:37:07.874 --> 00:37:10.954
how many unprecedented new things
are happening every moment?

00:37:11.553 --> 00:37:13.880
From Xiaogang's first stir
to the awakening of the Huangpu,

00:37:13.954 --> 00:37:16.633
which one isn't impacting
and refreshing our understanding?

00:37:16.874 --> 00:37:19.474
What we should do now
is to immerse into the masses

00:37:19.673 --> 00:37:21.834
to understand and investigate
every new thing,

00:37:21.994 --> 00:37:24.954
instead of being complacent
like our opponents,

00:37:25.153 --> 00:37:27.153
attempting to use
their existing knowledge system

00:37:27.233 --> 00:37:28.593
to judge these new things.

00:37:29.073 --> 00:37:30.314
You're twisting the argument.

00:37:30.633 --> 00:37:31.394
Our side believes

00:37:31.553 --> 00:37:32.914
it is exactly what you said

00:37:33.113 --> 00:37:35.994
that makes professional
journalistic gatekeeping necessary

00:37:36.113 --> 00:37:37.314
in this under-informed region.

00:37:37.394 --> 00:37:38.794
What makes you the gatekeeper?

00:37:39.113 --> 00:37:40.033
Who are you to decide

00:37:40.113 --> 00:37:42.794
what people should see or shouldn't see?

00:37:43.474 --> 00:37:44.274
Just last week,

00:37:44.513 --> 00:37:46.072
in the Yuehai Town of our province,

00:37:46.648 --> 00:37:48.113
their secretary apologized

00:37:48.314 --> 00:37:51.153
to over 1,000 cadres in an auditorium.

00:37:51.673 --> 00:37:52.274
He said,

00:37:52.513 --> 00:37:55.113
"When the interests of cadres
and the common people conflict,

00:37:55.474 --> 00:37:57.434
cadres must prioritize
the people's interests."

00:37:57.754 --> 00:37:58.354
Yes.

00:38:06.386 --> 00:38:09.434
