- Exactly.
- That's right.

00:39:13.834 --> 00:39:16.354
Don't rush the schedule just
to end up with subpar work quality.

00:39:17.073 --> 00:39:18.394
- Exactly!
- That's right!

00:39:18.754 --> 00:39:19.474
Ms. Li,

00:39:19.754 --> 00:39:21.354
once this road is finished,

00:39:21.834 --> 00:39:23.593
it'll be about as good
as Binhai Road, right?

